stream
BT
/F1 10.5 Tf
14 TL
1 0 0 1 54.0 738.0 Tm (CHURCH CAP QUICK START GUIDE) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 690.0 Tm (Version: 0.1.0 public preview) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 659.0 Tm (This guide is for the person setting up Church Cap for a church service.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 628.0 Tm (What Church Cap Does) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 580.0 Tm (Church Cap listens to one audio input from the church sound desk or USB audio interface.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 566.0 Tm (It creates live captions locally on the Mac and shares them over the church Wi-Fi.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 535.0 Tm (Visitors do not install an app. They scan a QR code and read captions in their browser.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 504.0 Tm (What You Need) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 456.0 Tm (- An Apple Silicon Mac, or a Windows 10/11 computer. On Windows, setup can offer to) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 442.0 Tm (install Python 3.12 if Windows Package Manager is available.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 428.0 Tm (- Church Cap downloaded or copied to the Mac.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 414.0 Tm (- Internet access for first setup.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 400.0 Tm (- A USB audio interface or mixer input from the sound desk.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 386.0 Tm (- The Mac and audience phones on a network where phones can reach the caption Mac.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 355.0 Tm (First-Time Setup On Mac) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 307.0 Tm (1. Open Terminal.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 293.0 Tm (2. Go to the Church Cap folder. This example assumes the folder has been moved into) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 279.0 Tm (Documents.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 248.0 Tm (cd "$HOME/Documents/church_cap_v0.1.0") Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 217.0 Tm (3. Run setup. Use `bash` for this first command because the setup script may not be) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 203.0 Tm (executable yet. The setup script repairs permissions for the other Church Cap scripts) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 189.0 Tm (automatically.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 158.0 Tm (bash setup-macos.sh) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 127.0 Tm (4. Wait for setup to finish, then continue to **Start Church Cap** below.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 96.0 Tm (The setup script installs the local Python environment, audio dependencies, and Argos) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 82.0 Tm (translation support/models. It only installs Python packages inside the Church Cap) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 68.0 Tm (folder's `.venv`.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
