4 0 obj
<< /Length 2167 >>
stream
BT
/F1 10.5 Tf
14 TL
1 0 0 1 54.0 738.0 Tm (If setup asks whether to set the Mac hostname to `church-cap.local`, choose yes if this) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 724.0 Tm (Mac will normally run captions.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 693.0 Tm (First-Time Setup On Windows) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 645.0 Tm (1. Open PowerShell.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 631.0 Tm (2. Go to the Church Cap folder. This example assumes the folder has been moved into) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 617.0 Tm (Documents.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 586.0 Tm (cd "$HOME\\Documents\\church_cap_v0.1.0") Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 555.0 Tm (3. Run setup.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 524.0 Tm (.\\setup-windows.cmd) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 493.0 Tm (4. Wait for setup to finish, then continue to **Start Church Cap** below.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 462.0 Tm (The setup script installs the local Python environment, app dependencies, Argos) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 448.0 Tm (translation support/models, and checks CUDA/GPU support. If Python is missing and) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 434.0 Tm (Windows Package Manager is available, setup can offer to install Python 3.12 first. If) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 420.0 Tm (an NVIDIA GPU is visible but CUDA runtime files are missing, setup can offer to install) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 406.0 Tm (local CUDA 12 runtime packages into Church Cap's `.venv`. If CUDA is not ready, Church) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 392.0 Tm (Cap falls back to CPU.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 361.0 Tm (You can also run the optional GPU runtime installer later:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 330.0 Tm (.\\install-cuda-runtime-windows.cmd) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 299.0 Tm (If Windows says `UnauthorizedAccess`, scripts are disabled, or the file came from) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 285.0 Tm (another computer, use `setup-windows.cmd`. If it is still blocked, right-click the) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 271.0 Tm (downloaded zip or Church Cap folder, choose **Properties**, tick **Unblock** if shown,) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 257.0 Tm (then try again.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 226.0 Tm (Start Church Cap) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 178.0 Tm (For normal use after setup:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 147.0 Tm (./start-macos.sh) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 116.0 Tm (On Windows:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 85.0 Tm (.\\start-windows.cmd) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 54.0 Tm (Wait while the app starts. The operator page should open automatically:) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
