1 0 0 1 54.0 721.0 Tm (http://localhost:9090/operator) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 690.0 Tm (On first Windows setup, Church Cap may open the password setup page first:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 659.0 Tm (http://localhost:9090/setup) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 628.0 Tm (The first time, create an operator password. Public caption viewers do not need this) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 614.0 Tm (password.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 583.0 Tm (Know The Two Ports) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 535.0 Tm (Church Cap normally uses two local ports:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 504.0 Tm (Operator controls: http://localhost:9090/operator) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 490.0 Tm (Audience captions: http://church-cap.local:8080/) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 459.0 Tm (If you accidentally open `localhost:8080/operator`, use `localhost:9090/operator`) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 445.0 Tm (instead.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 414.0 Tm (On Windows, audience phones usually use the IP address shown by `start-windows.cmd` or) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 400.0 Tm (the QR code on the operator page.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 369.0 Tm (Select The Audio Input) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 321.0 Tm (In the operator page:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 290.0 Tm (1. Stop captions if they are running.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 276.0 Tm (2. Find **Microphone / audio interface**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 262.0 Tm (3. Choose the USB audio interface or mixer input.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 248.0 Tm (4. Click **Save input**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 234.0 Tm (5. Click **Start captions**.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 203.0 Tm (Recommended audio route:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 172.0 Tm (Church microphones -> sound desk -> USB audio interface -> Church Cap Mac) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 141.0 Tm (Avoid using the built-in Mac microphone for a church service.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 110.0 Tm (Share Captions With Visitors) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 62.0 Tm (In the operator page, open **Audience & OBS**.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
