1 0 0 1 54.0 721.0 Tm (Common Problems) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 673.0 Tm (The operator page does not open) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 642.0 Tm (Use:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 611.0 Tm (http://localhost:9090/operator) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 580.0 Tm (Wait a few seconds after running `./start-macos.sh`.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 549.0 Tm (The audience QR code does not open on a phone) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 518.0 Tm (Use the Android/IP fallback QR code on the operator page. Also check that the phone is) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 504.0 Tm (on the same network and that guest Wi-Fi is allowed to reach the caption Mac.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 473.0 Tm (No audio devices appear) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 442.0 Tm (- Check the USB audio interface is connected.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 428.0 Tm (- Check macOS microphone permissions.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 414.0 Tm (- Run setup again if PortAudio was not installed.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 383.0 Tm (Captions are inaccurate) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 352.0 Tm (- Use a direct feed from the sound desk rather than the built-in microphone.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 338.0 Tm (- Check audio level.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 324.0 Tm (- Add common corrections to `config/glossary.csv`.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 310.0 Tm (- Use the bad-word censor for likely speech-to-text mistakes.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 279.0 Tm (You need to stop Church Cap) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 248.0 Tm (Press `Ctrl+C` in the Terminal window running Church Cap.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 217.0 Tm (Privacy Reminder) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 169.0 Tm (AI-generated captions can contain mistakes. Use the sensitive blank/pause mode for) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 155.0 Tm (private or pastoral moments. Churches should use clear notices and follow their own) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 141.0 Tm (safeguarding, privacy, and data protection policies.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 110.0 Tm (Feedback) Tj
1 0 0 1 54.0 62.0 Tm (The operator page includes a **Feedback** link. Use it for feature ideas, issues, setup) Tj
ET
endstream
